Name: Fruit Crackle
AttributesDescription: Grants 30% Heavy Attack DMG Bonus to all Resonators in the team for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: A snack made from Dusk Honeypots coated in frozen syrup. It gets its name from the cracking sound you hear when you bite into it. It’s a favorite among Royan children, though it takes some skill to crunch on the sugarcoat while keeping the berry’s juice from spilling onto your clothes.
